Posts.Content: Forgive me, but this is not a question directly related to cancer but it is related to the breast. This was the closest forum I could find relating to my post. The pores on my breasts when squeezed secrete pus like a whitehead or something. Is this normal? I don't have any lumps on my breasts, and there is no discharge from my nipples. Thanks for reading. -Shanni
